                  <bindingDesc>
                     <binding notBefore="1982" notAfter="1982" contemporary="false">
                        <p>Band frá 1982 (<dimensions type="binding">
                              <height>230</height>
                              <width>180</width>
                              <depth>10</depth>
                           </dimensions>). Spjöld og kjölur klædd fínofnum líndúki. Saumað á móttök. Tvö saurblöð úr bandi.</p>
